{"word":"G4032 - περικρύπτω - perikrýptō - per-ee-kroop'-to - Hide","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περικρύπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">perikrýptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">per-ee-kroop'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Hide</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வெளிப்படாதிருப்பது - வினைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"to conceal on all sides or entirely, to hide, to keep oneself at home"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4012 - περί - perí - per-ee'/4012\">G4012</a> and <a href=\"#/G2928 - κρύπτω - krýptō - kroop'-to/2928\">G2928</a>; to <i>conceal</i> all <i>around</i>, that is, <i>entirely:</i> - hide.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}